kquote><br />\n我自己就熱氣就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f8c83e73e25273fe03de9ba4e823df59bff4b9","tid":121424,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T00:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>條利生飛吱先係最痛果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申2-3個月生一次 <br />\n每次十幾pat飛吱係口腔同利到</blockquote><br />\n我呢粒有手指尾咁大粒 係正喉嚨兩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚high</blockquote><br />\n我試過五粒生正喉嚨定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住係得呢一次咁岩幾粒生埋同一個位<br />\n點知高處未算高 唔知點解中三開始每2-3個月就生成十幾粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打好番未？曾經同你一樣 一粒未完一粒又黎<br />\n仲有自殺嘅念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自從用左漱口水之後 就好少生<br />\n有隻漱口水寫住有效治療飛滋 可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有諗過自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果排係條利兩邊腫哂<br />\n口腔兩邊爛哂有少少朧 上下唇幾粒<br />\n牙肉腫 等等<br />\n係連開口都覺得痛<br />\n漱口水試過一啲得一啲唔得 主要都係用醫生開個啲 坊間買到既多數唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我陣間都準備睇醫生 好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想吞口水"},{"pid":"82459e81a4a34c4dfd3448a6b69dfcc2fdc4e5c2","tid":121424,"uid":1447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T00:40:25.000Z","msg":"2-3星期就生一粒<br />\n依家有時生左都冇乜感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38f3a689bcbcc6c481d1e59cbf48333082cd411","tid":121424,"uid":77730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T00:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>條利生飛吱先係最痛果隻<img 